videos.headline: Antoine cuts across entire field for incredible FAU TD
videos.description: FAU's Deangelo Antoine chugs to the house for his third receiving touchdown of the half as he jets across the field en route to a 28-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Antoine cuts across entire field for incredible FAU TD) 2019/9/21 ESHEET
